<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('partials/head', { seo }) %>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero hero--subtle">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <span class="eyebrow">Business Plan</span>
          <h1>Bhojan Mitra roadmap for investors & founding partners</h1>
          <p>See how voice-first ordering, AI recommendations, and IoT routing come together in the next 18 months. We’re building alongside early restaurants to prove throughput, accuracy, and guest experience wins.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="https://billing.aarohitavigyan.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Apply for the pilot</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">Book an investor briefing</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="products">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Focus areas</span>
        <h2>Three tracks drive Bhojan Mitra’s product thesis</h2>
        <div class="products-grid">
          <div class="product-card">
            <h3>Voice + AI</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Accent-aware speech models tuned on Indian restaurant dialogs</li>
              <li>Contextual upsells, modifiers, and allergy prompts</li>
              <li>Human-in-the-loop review workflows for peak hours</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="product-card featured">
            <h3>IoT Routing</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Kitchen display orchestration plus smart printer routing</li>
              <li>Device SDK for existing POS terminals and tablets</li>
              <li>Offline-first buffer so orders never stop flowing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="product-card">
            <h3>Analytics + Ops</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Menu intelligence, item-level profitability, shift performance</li>
              <li>Chain-ready controls for multi-location rollouts</li>
              <li>API-first approach for partner integrations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ecosystem">
      <div class="container">
        <span class="eyebrow">18 month roadmap</span>
        <h2>Milestones across product, go-to-market, and operations</h2>
        <div class="ecosystem-grid">
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Phase 1 — Pilot validation</h3>
            <p>Voice accuracy benchmarks with 5 pilot restaurants, IoT routing beta, and revenue-share agreements for founding partners.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card featured">
            <h3>Phase 2 — Product scaling</h3>
            <p>Analytics suite GA, regional language packs, kitchen hardware bundles, and self-serve onboarding for QSR brands.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="eco-card">
            <h3>Phase 3 — Expansion</h3>
            <p>Marketplace integrations, franchise-ready deployment playbooks, and strategic city-level rollouts.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Request the full Bhojan Mitra business brief</h2>
        <p>We share detailed traction metrics, pilot results, and financial projections under NDA. Let’s explore how we can build the voice-led POS category together.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions center">
          <a href="mailto:kanhaiya@aarohitavigyan.com" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Email kanhaiya@aarohitavigyan.com</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">Book a 1:1 session</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
